{"tid":2047170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【正視聽】不要被共產黨轉移注意力，局勢重點不在明州！","createTime":"2020-06-02T02:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T05:45:58.000Z","uid":109589,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a23caf031c1d0b4fbc46099986b55fbf3f87f457","tid":2047170,"uid":109589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T02:21:34.000Z","msg":"1，無論是人數規模，抗爭水平，抗爭訴求，香港和明尼蘇達州完全沒有可比性。<br />\n2，香港人是爭取民主，捍衛自由，而有色人種是反對種族歧視，風馬牛不相及。<br />\n3，涉事警察已經有了法律上的後續，目前港警無一人入罪。<br />\n4，明州徹頭徹尾是美國領土，屬於美國內政，而香港問題並不是共產黨內政。<br />\n5，香港問題是中美衝突的產物，是民主自由和獨裁專制之間的敵我矛盾，而明州事件是民主國家的內部矛盾。<br />\n6，當大家稍把關注放在美國的時候，共產黨正在加大力度在香港抓人。<br />\n7，香港人非常守法，是政府違法。<br />\n8，美國什麼風浪都見過，沒這麼脆弱。<br />\n9，與其關心民主國家內政，不如討論一下如何讓獨裁者不配有內政。<br />\n10，美國人再慘也比中國人過得好，美國警察再猛也比共產黨好。<br />\n<br />\n轉自<br />\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/19844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpincong.rocks%2Farticle%2F19844&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbcg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=7f9a14bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/article/19844</a>"},{"pid":"11b0f77a96fdc3db6c5413b32f3954785944fcdc","tid":2047170,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T02:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2115e98f4265b1b684dbc81804d6034630d0f763","tid":2047170,"uid":53742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4db2804dd777ea7687a17d6ad45c0f848f615d63","tid":2047170,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T02:23:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e12186b9aafa596c3db3e67dfa663a4180577bd3","tid":2047170,"uid":55005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T02:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33315002172b792a163ea97d8ca11f7934a041f0","tid":2047170,"uid":109589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T02:33:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00be928c72475f76929894cbeb964d345d622d3f","tid":2047170,"uid":19617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T02:37:30.000Z","msg":"美國警暴起因係種族歧視，咁香港啲人反警暴又係為咗乜？ 呢樣我覺得幾重要，希望大家有共識"},{"pid":"0b95374e5b6e4272e59cf8f920744ffc26106d58","tid":2047170,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}